@startuml sd_ReportService_getYearlyComparison
skinparam backgroundColor #F9FAFB
title ReportService.getYearlyComparison(year) - 年度工资对比分析

actor "调用方" as Client
participant "ReportController" as Ctrl
participant "ReportService" as RptSvc
participant "DepartmentRepository" as DeptRepo
participant "SalaryRecordRepository" as RecRepo

Client -> Ctrl: GET /api/reports/yearly-comparison?year=2024
Ctrl -> RptSvc: getYearlyComparison(year)
RptSvc -> DeptRepo: findByActiveTrue()
DeptRepo --> RptSvc: List<Department> (5个部门)
note right of RptSvc #F0F8FF
  **双重遍历:**
  for each 部门:
    for m = 1 to 12:
      ym = "2024" + "01"~"12"
      查询该部门该月记录
      汇总应发+实发
end note
loop 每个部门
  loop 1月~12月
    RptSvc -> RecRepo: findByYearMonthAndDepartment(ym, deptId)
    RecRepo --> RptSvc: List<SalaryRecord>
    alt 有记录
      RptSvc -> RptSvc: new YearlyComparisonDto(deptName, ym,\ngrossPay, netPay)
    end
  end
end
RptSvc --> Ctrl: List<YearlyComparisonDto>\n[ {部门:技术部, 月份:202401, 应发:50000, 实发:40000}, ... ]
Ctrl --> Client: ApiResponse → JSON\n(可用于前端ECharts折线图)
@enduml
